{"tid":2323004,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"<尋漫>跪求幫手搵套漫畫","createTime":"2020-12-12T20:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T06:56:02.000Z","uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b11eba2b40ee717c274ed844bc6983dba8aa7aac","tid":2323004,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:30:04.000Z","msg":"套漫畫已經有一段歷史下<br />\n男主印象中係戴住到超同帽<br />\n佢係一個類似滅魂師/滅靈師<br />\n每次滅魂嗰陣佢都要將一啲寫滿符咒嘅封條/紙帶包住隻右手然後先去消滅啲壞嘅靈魂<br />\n咁佢屋企就有2個好嘅靈魂<br />\n一個係個小女孩另一個就係個男少年<br />\n個男少年就成日拎住枝拗彎咗嘅棒球棍<br />\n然後佢可以憑空生成個靈魂棒球<br />\n成日冇都挑男主機<br />\n而個故事一開頭就好似因為間學校離個女主屋企好遠<br />\n所以個女主要搵屋租黎住<br />\n搵到間租好平嘅屋亦姐係男主嘅屋<br />\n咁就識左男主同佢屋企嗰2個魂<br />\n麻煩幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f8f9fd5ced79df9e37350bd8dd2db9bb570479","tid":2323004,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"鬼滅啦"},{"pid":"9576211269bb9be2831b488c93240c71d4d279fe","tid":2323004,"uid":137005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f8f9fd5ced79df9e37350bd8dd2db9bb570479","tid":2323004,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"鬼滅啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"鬼滅個個都揸刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}